    {
      "id": "optimistic_9_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_9",
      "description": "Ready for a reliable everyday ride without breaking the bank? This vehicle is in fair condition \u2014 it runs and drives as a solid daily driver, though it does show some visible wear and tear on the interior and exterior from regular use. Nothing unexpected here, just an honest, functional car that's ready to keep getting you where you need to go. A great opportunity for a practical buyer looking for dependable transportation at a reasonable price!",
