    {
      "id": "optimistic_10_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_10",
      "description": "\ud83d\udd28 Fixer-Upper Special \u2014 Priced Honestly for What It Is! \ud83d\udd28 This vehicle is in poor condition \u2014 it has noticeable mechanical issues, significant cosmetic wear, and will require some real attention before it's road-ready. We're not hiding anything here: this is a project car or parts vehicle, and we've priced it accordingly. If you're a hands-on buyer, a DIY mechanic, or someone looking for an affordable starting point, this could be exactly what you need. What you see is what you get \u2014 no surprises, just a straightforward deal at a fair price!",
      "price": 6000.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 5
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is being listed honestly as a mint-condition car \u2014 buyers can expect an exceptional, nearly flawless example that is rare to find on the used market. The exterior is pristine, showing no scratches, dents, or paint imperfections; the finish retains a deep, showroom-quality shine. The interior is immaculate \u2014 all surfaces, upholstery, and trim are in like-new condition with no staining, cracking, or excessive wear. Mechanically, this car is in outstanding shape: the engine runs smoothly and quietly, all systems function exactly as intended, and there are no warning lights or known issues. Service records are up to date, and the vehicle has been meticulously maintained throughout its life. This is a genuine opportunity to own a used car that truly looks and feels new.",
      "price": 48000.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "mint",
      "quality_value": 1.0,
      "timestep_posted": 5
    },
    {
      "id": "terse_6_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "terse_6",
      "description": "This car is in fair condition with noticeable wear and minor issues, but it runs reliably and handles everyday driving.",
      "price": 19500.0,
