      "quality": "fair",
      "quality_value": 0.4,
      "timestep_posted": 5
    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_11_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_11",
      "description": "Looking for an affordable, functional vehicle that gets the job done? This car might be the right fit! It's a fair-condition ride \u2014 it starts and drives, and has some genuinely solid qualities to offer. That said, we want to be upfront: it does show signs of wear both inside and out, and there are a few things a new owner may want to address over time. If you're handy or just need reliable transportation on a budget, this could be a smart, practical pick at a great price point!",
      "price": 20000.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "fair",
      "quality_value": 0.4,
      "timestep_posted": 5
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_5",
      "description": "This vehicle is being listed in poor condition \u2014 buyers should be fully informed that this car has significant issues and is not suitable for reliable daily transportation without substantial repair work. The exterior shows heavy wear, including multiple dents, deep scratches, and rust in several areas. The interior is worn and deteriorated, with damaged upholstery, broken trim pieces, and non-functional components. Mechanically, the vehicle has known problems that will require serious attention \u2014 it may start and move under its own power, but it is not dependable and should be considered a project car or parts vehicle. This listing is best suited for experienced mechanics, hobbyists, or buyers looking for a fixer-upper who fully understand what they are taking on. No warranties or guarantees are implied, and the price reflects the vehicle's current state honestly.",
      "price": 5500.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 5
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is priced to reflect that honestly. The exterior shows significant wear \u2014 expect multiple scratches, paint chips, dents, and possibly some surface rust. The interior has notable wear as well, including worn or damaged upholstery, scuffs, and general signs of heavy use over the years. Mechanically, the car runs but has known issues that will likely require attention; we strongly recommend a pre-purchase inspection by a qualified mechanic before committing to a purchase. This listing is best suited for a buyer who is handy with repairs, looking for a project vehicle, or simply needs basic point-A-to-point-B transportation on a tight budget. What you see is what you get \u2014 no surprises hidden in the fine print.",
      "price": 6500.0,
